---
title: Quick Double Honey-Soy & Ginger Pork Meatballs with Ponzu Slaw & Peanuts
description: Fragrance, aromas and flavours, we can tick all those boxes with these pork meatballs. The honey-soy glaze adds a touch of sweet and salty goodness, perfect for ginger pork meatballs. That’s a wrap on our dinner to-do list!

